<h1 className={"openapi__heading"}>Add elements in bulk</h1>

<MethodEndpoint method={"post"} path={"/v1/lookup-lists/{lookupListId}/elements/bulk-add"}></MethodEndpoint>



Adds an array of elements to an existing Lookup list and sets the expiration date for the lookup. 
Please ensure to change the region in the URL to match your account's region.
